agers]]\n[[Category:Animated television series about twins]]\n[[Category:Canadian animated television programs featuring anthropomorphic characters]]\n[[Category:Canadian children's animated action television series]]\n[[Category:Canadian children's animated adventure television series]]\n[[Category:Canadian children's animated comic science fiction television series]]\n[[Category:Canadian children's animated science fantasy television series]]\n[[Category:Canadian flash animated television series]]\n[[Category:English-language television programs]]\n[[Category:CW4Kids original programs]]\n[[Category:Kids' WB original programs]]\n[[Category:Teletoon original series]]\n[[Category:Family Channel shows]]\n[[Category:Middle school television series]]\n[[Category:Television series by Cookie Jar Entertainment]]\n[[Category:Television series by DHX Media]]\n[[Category:Television series by Warner Bros. Animation]]\n[[Category:Television series by Corus Entertainment]]\n[[Category:Television series created by Scott Fellows]]\n[[Category:Television series produced in Ontario]]\n[[Category:Television series produced in Nova Scotia]]\n", "text_old": "{{Distinguish|John Test}}\n{{About||the video game|Johnny Test (video game)}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name            = '''Johnny Test'''\n| image                = Johnny Test Logo.jpg\n| genre                = [[Science fantasy]]<br />[[Action fiction|Action]]<br>[[Adventure fiction|Adventure]]<br />[[Comedy]]\n| creator              = [[Scott Fellows]]\n| developer            = [[Aaron Simpson (producer)|Aaron Simpson]]\n| voices               = {{Plainlist|\n* [[James Arnold Taylor]]\n* [[Louis Chirillo]] <small>(seasons 1\u20134)</small>\n* [[Trevor Devall]] <small>(seasons 5\u20136)</small>\n*  Brittney Wilson <small>(seasons 1, 5)</small>\n* [[Ashleigh Ball]] <small>(seasons 2\u20134, 6)</small>\n* [[Maryke Hendrikse]]\n* [[Ian James Corlett]]\n* [[Kathleen Barr]]\n* [[Lee Tockar]]\n* [[Andrew Francis]]\n* [[Bill Mondy]